{
  "texts": [
    "In both cases, the codon language model shows comparable or better performance to the best language models, and outperforms all language models of similar parameter count.",
    "We report performance using the Pearson correlation coefficient between predicted and true values.",
    "Data are presented as mean values with error bars representing the standard deviation calculated from fivefold cross-validation.",
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s42256-024-00791-0",
    "(data code 'CON')."
  ]
}